sweet / easy lucene_29 wrapper

Implemented (abstract) base class provided, for both storage and RAM indexing.

I used this for a Hadoop environment with RAM indeces buit from SSD pdf files

sweetlucene.dll v0.95

sample usage:

SweetLuceneWrapper wrapper1 = new SweetLuceneWrapper();            
TextBox1.Text = wrapper1.LucGo(index: true, 
                               ramindex: false, 
                               search: true, 
                               lookinside: true, 
                               path: @"c:\temp", 
                               queryStr: "brokebloke", 
                               fileExtensionsToIndex: new List<string>() { ".txt" });
